NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
As the U.S. Open tennis tournament approaches its climax, former Swedish star 
Bjorn Borg was drawing a different kind of crowd in Milan, Italy. 
</P>
<P>
His five-minute wedding ceremony with Italian pop singer Loredana Berte at the 
city hall was preceded by a brawl between the couple's private security guards 
and reporters and photographers who were barred from the ceremony. An Italian 
weekly magazine was given exclusive rights to the story. 
</P>
