<HEADLINE>
<P>
EMERGENCY-ROOM PHYSICIAN FOCUSES ON A FILM CAREERPHYSICIANDOCTORSMOTION 
PICTURESAWARDSMOTION PICTURE DIRECTORSCAREERSSTUDENTSGENTILE, LANCE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By FELICIA PAIK 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Dr. Lance Gentile in his film "Stat," on the emotional cost of working 
in trauma care, winner of a Nissan FOCUS award. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
